Package: zzmesoimpute
Title: Imputation Strategies for Below-Detection-Limit Assay Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ronald (Ryy) G", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: Methods for imputing left-censored (below limit of detection)
    concentrations from multiplexed immunoassays such as Meso Scale Discovery
    (MSD). Provides a common interface across substitution, uniform-draw,
    regression-on-order-statistics, censored maximum-likelihood, and multiple
    imputation strategies for benchmarking and applied use.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
URL: https://github.com/rgt47/zzmesoimpute
BugReports: https://github.com/rgt47/zzmesoimpute/issues
Imports:
    readxl,
    stats
Suggests:
    tinytest (>= 1.4.0),
    writexl
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
